HEADER:

The header is sent for all non-payload packets after 4 ZERO-bytes

      0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
   0 ! Version       ! Crypt-Version ! Packet Type   ! Flags         !
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+

Packet Types: pre-handshake, handshake, holepunch
Flags: ACK (acknowledge)

SN_HEADER:

the SN header is sent for all payload packets going to or coming from the
supernode

      0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
   0 ! Version       ! Crypt-Version ! Packet Type   ! Flags         !
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+

Packet Types: supernode_register, keep_alive, address_resolution,
	      edge_connect, edge_resume
Flags: ACK (acknowledge)



--------------------

SN_Flag = DH_INIT

      0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
   4 ! HMAC_IV + DH Values (ECDH or g, p, A) + KDF_SALT_A + HMAC
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+

SN_Flag = DH_INIT + ACK

      0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
   4 ! HMAC_IV + DH Values (ECDH or B) + KDF_SALT_S + HMAC
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+

If the DH_INIT flag is not set, the rest of the packet (payload) will be in a
cryptographic container of the following format:

      0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
   4 ! 12 Byte AEAD_IV ...                                           :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
   8 : ...                                                           :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  12 : ...                                              ... AEAD_IV  !
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
     : PAYLOAD X BYTES
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
   Y : 16 Byte AEAD_ICV ...
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
 Y+4 : ...                                                           :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
 Y+8 : ...                                                           :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
 Y+12: ...                                             ... AEAD_ICV  :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+


all that follows is contained in the encrypted and authenticated payload

SN_FLAG = REG
    This is the payload inside the crypto container:

      0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  16 ! Community ...                                                 :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  20 : ... Community ...                                             :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  24 : ... Community ...                                             :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  28 : ... Community                                                 !
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  32 ! MAC address ...                                               :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  36 : ... MAC address ...           ! IP Address ...
     +-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+-+

SN_Flag = REG + ACK
    This is the payload inside the crypto container:

      0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  16 ! Public Socket ...                                             :
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  20 : ... Public Socket                                             !
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  24 ! TODO: what else?                                              !
     +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+

